  "body": "Output of `helm version`: version.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.0.0\", GitCommit:\"e29ce2a54e96cd02ccfce88bee4f58bb6e2a28b6\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", GoVersion:\"go1.13.4\"}\r\n\r\n\r\nWith helm v2, passing --username myname to helm repo add caused helm to interactively ask for a password which is positive for security reasons (not having a password show up in process lists and shell histories, the password being shadowed while entering).\r\n\r\nhelm v3 seems to have lost this ability, which looks like a regression to me.\r\n",
